  <description><![CDATA[<p>Start your stay in the famous resort of Chamonix, moving on to Zermatt via the picturesque Mont Blanc Express railway journey. For an extended stay, continue on to Grindelwald in the Bernese Oberland and explore two or three famous resorts in awe-inspiring settings linked by one of the most spectacular rail journeys across the Alps.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-france/iconic-mountains-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-france/iconic-mountains-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-france/iconic-mountains-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-france/iconic-mountains-tour#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-france/iconic-mountains-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
